divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home from work down a road to my house and i looked up to the left and saw a very bright light, too bright to be an airplane. I continued down the road and it started moving down very fast and 4 distinct lights appeared on the corners in the shape of a diamond. I kept watching it until it disappeared behind the treeline, and then watched it move back up. I was very excited to see this because I have been following UFO cases for 3 years now and I finally get to see one.
